  <brief_title>Berberine and Altered Fasting Glucose</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of the Assumption of a Berberine Phytosoma-based Supplement on the Hematic Values of Glucose in a Group of Patients With Altered Fasting Glucose</official_title>
