  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study was to evaluate the effectiveness of a food supplement, berberine&#xD;
      phytosome, which contributes to the control of blood sugar and the improvement of insulin&#xD;
      resistance.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
